00:22:15.070 --> 00:22:15.080
coming.'Most

00:22:15.080 --> 00:22:16.910
of the church knows. Well, the

00:22:16.920 --> 00:22:18.550
ones I hang around, at least we all talk

00:22:18.560 --> 00:22:19.480
