00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:47.550
earth:

00:22:47.560 --> 00:22:49.350
a

00:22:49.360 --> 00:22:51.510
shaking in politics,

00:22:51.520 --> 00:22:54.230
a shaking in finances,

00:22:54.240 --> 00:22:56.870
a shaking in the earth's crust and

00:22:56.880 --> 00:23:00.190
earthquakes, a shaking in the

00:23:00.200 --> 00:23:03.030
