00:23:58.480 --> 00:24:00.550
They're coming in hot,

00:24:00.550 --> 00:24:00.560
Braden.'And

00:24:00.560 --> 00:24:02.510
so I just

00:24:02.520 --> 00:24:04.190
keep trying to tell you and sounding the

00:24:04.200 --> 00:24:05.470
