00:24:41.230 --> 00:24:41.240
D,

00:24:41.240 --> 00:24:42.710
I said, 'We've got to

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:45.070
come up higher in our confession. We've

00:24:45.080 --> 00:24:46.550
got to come up higher in what we're

00:24:46.560 --> 00:24:47.710
saying

00:24:47.720 --> 00:24:50.310
because

00:24:50.320 --> 00:24:51.350
life and death is in the power of

00:24:51.350 --> 00:24:51.360
the

00:24:51.360 --> 00:24:52.550
tongue. But

00:24:52.560 --> 00:24:54.390
as a man thinketh in his heart, so is

00:24:54.400 --> 00:24:56.830
