00:24:56.840 --> 00:24:58.150
of the abundance of the heart, the mouth

00:24:58.160 --> 00:25:00.070
speaks.

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:01.710
And what you're saying is what you're

00:25:01.720 --> 00:25:04.190
living today. What you said yesterday is

00:25:04.200 --> 00:25:05.750
what you're going to live. What you said

00:25:05.760 --> 00:25:07.230
today is what you live tomorrow or the

00:25:07.240 --> 00:25:09.550
next day. But what you keep saying out

00:25:09.560 --> 00:25:11.030
of your mouth because your tongue... the Bible says the tongue is the pen of a ready writer. I believe your

00:25:11.040 --> 00:25:13.750
tongue

00:25:13.750 --> 00:25:13.760
is

00:25:15.990 --> 00:25:16.000
the

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:18.710
pen

00:25:18.720 --> 00:25:20.750
of a ready

00:25:20.760 --> 00:25:23.070
writer. You're writing your ticket.

00:25:23.080 --> 00:25:26.390
You're writing what you're

00:25:26.390 --> 00:25:26.400
living.'What

00:25:26.400 --> 00:25:27.669
