00:26:07.679 --> 00:26:10.910
care what you say. I believe that my God

00:26:10.920 --> 00:26:13.830
is an abundant supply. He supplies all

00:26:13.840 --> 00:26:15.550
my needs.'The doctor comes and

00:26:15.560 --> 00:26:17.350
gives you a bad report.

00:26:17.360 --> 00:26:18.910
The doctor says you

00:26:18.910 --> 00:26:18.920
have four

